{"id": 2292, "name": "Projet de loi de financement de la s\u00e9curit\u00e9 sociale pour 2025, n\u00b0\u00a0325", "url": "/dyn/17/amendements/0325/AN/2292", "date": "2024-10-25", "status": "Adopt\u00e9", "proposed_by": [{"first_name": "Sandrine", "last_name": "Josso", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Marc", "last_name": "Fesneau", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Romain", "last_name": "Daubi\u00e9", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Cyrille", "last_name": "Isaac-Sibille", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Philippe", "last_name": "Vigier", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Nicolas", "last_name": "Turquois", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Sabine", "last_name": "Thillaye", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Richard", "last_name": "Ramos", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Josy", "last_name": "Poueyto", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Maud", "last_name": "Petit", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric", "last_name": "Petit", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Jimmy", "last_name": "Pahun", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Didier", "last_name": "Padey", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Hubert", "last_name": "Ott", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Louise", "last_name": "Morel", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Sophie", "last_name": "Mette", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Paul", "last_name": "Mattei", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9ric", "last_name": "Martineau", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Mandon", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Delphine", "last_name": "Lingemann", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Pascal", "last_name": "Lecamp", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Philippe", "last_name": "Latombe", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Fabien", "last_name": "Lain\u00e9", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Frantz", "last_name": "Gumbs", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Carles", "last_name": "Grelier", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Perrine", "last_name": "Goulet", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Bruno", "last_name": "Fuchs", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Olivier", "last_name": "Falorni", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Laurent", "last_name": "Croizier", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Micka\u00ebl", "last_name": "Cosson", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Blandine", "last_name": "Brocard", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Philippe", "last_name": "Bolo", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Christophe", "last_name": "Blanchet", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Anne", "last_name": "Bergantz", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "G\u00e9raldine", "last_name": "Bannier", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}, {"first_name": "Erwan", "last_name": "Balanant", "party": "Les D\u00e9mocrates"}], "summary": "Cet amendement a pour objet de permettre une exp\u00e9rimentation, appel\u00e9e par le Conseil national de l\u2019ordre des m\u00e9decins (CNOM), pour rendre accessibles et remboursables les tests permettant de d\u00e9tecter une soumission chimique, y compris sans d\u00e9p\u00f4t de plainte, pour am\u00e9liorer la prise en charge des potentielles victimes.\nLa soumission chimique consiste \u00e0 administrer des substances psychoactives \u00e0\u00a0une personne \u00e0 son insu ou sous la menace, \u00e0 des fins d\u00e9lictuelles ou criminelles. Or, le co\u00fbt des analyses toxicologiques pour permettre de d\u00e9tecter \u00e0 temps ces substances peut\u00a0atteindre jusqu\u2019\u00e0 1\u00a0000\u00a0euros. Et l\u2019unique fa\u00e7on de voir ces tests rembours\u00e9s est de d\u00e9poser plainte. Or, les d\u00e9p\u00f4ts de plaintes ne sont pas syst\u00e9matiques, notamment en raison des amn\u00e9sies caus\u00e9es par les substances ing\u00e9r\u00e9es.\nCes tests ne peuvent \u00eatre r\u00e9alis\u00e9s que dans des laboratoires de toxicologie experts. \u00a0Aussi, prendre en charge ces tests sur prescription m\u00e9dicale par le biais de l\u2019Assurance-maladie permettrait d\u2019encourager plus de victimes \u00e0 se faire d\u00e9pister rapidement, et ainsi de renforcer leur acc\u00e8s \u00e0 la justice et aux soins appropri\u00e9s.\nL\u2019adoption de cet amendement d\u2019exp\u00e9rimentation permettrait d'enfin prendre en compte la gravit\u00e9 et l\u2019urgence de ce probl\u00e8me."}